		</Group>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="114" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士将在高空召唤5枚陨落的拟造古月遗骸，依次向地面落去，并造成<span color="#b8b8b8">70%</span><span>伤害；该技能为持久技，期间博士可施放其他技能。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1567" width="440" height="114" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">若博士受到超过自身<span color="#ffdfbf">20%</span><span>生命值的单次伤害，则立即进入高伤遏制状态，全抗提升</span><span color="#ffdfbf">150%</span><span>，持续3.5s，并恢复期间损失的生命值，不超过</span><span color="#ffdfbf">33%</span><span>生命值上限。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1288" width="444" height="289" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">拟造古月遗骸：位于其后方可避免秒杀，处于该处时为全队提供元素能量与特殊能量的<span color="#ffdfbf">持续恢复</span><span>。<br/>秒杀机理：不同于其他秒杀，该秒杀为造成多次</span><span color="#ffdfbf">70%生命值</span><span>的伤害。<br/>月拟造影：博士召唤物，生命值</span><span color="#ffdfbf">267122</span><span>(7.2F)，攻击力</span><span color="#ffdfbf">12180</span><span>(6.4B2)，在「异界」内体现生命值，在常规场地体现攻击力。<br/>蚀月领域：不断扩张的红色圆形，扩张完毕耗时20s，半径最大可达10m，角色位于其中会降低</span><span color="#ffdfbf">40%</span><span>移速。<br/>异界裂隙：蚀月领域扩张至4.5m(9s)时出现，进入期间会出现与裂隙同位的月拟造影，清除相应造影可移除相应位置的蚀月领域并退出空间，或者自寻出口逃脱。<br/>E：环境反应等级系数，90级时为1202.81。<br/>若想被投影仪抓起，双方等级差同样需要</span><span fontFamily="SDK_JP_Web">≤</span><span>20级。<br/>高伤遏制机制CD为30s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士朝前方及两侧方向迅速发射水柱，均造成<span color="#7fbfff">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士在近处进行至多2段普攻：钉锁造成<span color="#ffacff">40%</span><span>伤害；水柱向前方及两侧方向造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">60%</span><span>伤害；可单独施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1119" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士在近处进行3段普攻：钉锁造成<span color="#ffacff">20%</span><span>伤害，并向前产生3道游走激光；冰钉挥舞造成</span><span color="#99ffff">40%</span><span>伤害；水柱仅向前方造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="426" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士朝天，持续降雨造成<span color="#7fbfff">20%</span><span>伤害；8s后，博士倒放降雨，升起的雨滴也造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">20%</span><span>伤害，随后于中央产生巨大水花，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士突然向左侧滑动，并发射数道激流，持续造成<span color="#7fbfff">20%</span><span>伤害，随后博士会根据距离，后接「矫锋诡剂未曾试」的某一段攻击</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士召唤2个「月拟造影」，其将移动至玩家周围，进行一次攻击后消失，造成3段月拟造影<span color="#99ffff">20%</span><span>攻击力的伤害。也常作为古月惩罚的偷袭技能。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1343" width="439" height="344" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士在场地边界召唤3个「<span textDecoration="underline">月拟造影</span><span>」，造成4~5段</span><span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span color="#99ffff">E</span><span>攻击力的伤害，同时产生不断扩张的「</span><span textDecoration="underline">蚀月领域</span><span>」，该领域初始产生冰脉冲，随着领域范围扩张，冰脉冲的威力也逐渐加强：<br/>初始造成</span><span color="#99ffff">150%E</span><span>伤害，扩张至约一半半径后出现「</span><span textDecoration="underline">异界裂隙</span><span>」，随后脉冲伤害提升至</span><span color="#99ffff">300%E</span><span>，扩张结束一段时间后冰脉冲频率翻倍，伤害提升至</span><span color="#99ffff">450%E</span><span>。<br/>「异界裂隙」内游走的激光持续造成</span><span color="#ffacff">80%E</span><span>的真伤。若未完全清除「蚀月领域」，则博士不再尝试生成新的领域。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1119" width="407" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士操纵三月权能，对玩家施加干扰：<br/><span color="#f1a3be">虹月</span><span>：角色不可面向博士，持续6s；<br/></span><span color="#a5e4f8">霜月</span><span>：角色不能大幅移动，持续6s；<br/></span><span color="#c4f2f8">恒月</span><span>：角色水平移动反转，持续6s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1343" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">违反博士的三月干扰将触发惩罚：清空全队所有能量，并被投影仪抓起，造成<span color="#99ffff">10%x4+50%</span><span>伤害；遵循三月干扰则恢复全队所有能量。</span><span color="#ffbfbf">恒月干扰为始终遵循</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/博士.assets/Image_16.png')" x="88" y="224" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<Group d:userLabel="Group_2">
			<RichText x="75" y="1179" fontFamily="汉仪润圆-65W" fontSize="25" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ff9999" width="42" height="29" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
				<content>
					<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="汉仪润圆-65W" fontSize="25" color="#ff9999">210</p>
