		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="441" height="114" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士立即升空，召唤3枚「<span textDecoration="underline">拟造古月遗骸</span><span>」落地，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">20%</span><span>伤害；6s后，博士汇聚月矩力发动月陨冲击，不处于「遗骸」后方扇区的目标将立即被</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffbfbf">秒杀</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/博士.assets/Image_29.png')" x="722" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士锚定玩家，从自身游离出6个背向博士的游走激光，接触造成<span color="#ffacff">20%,10%,5%,<br/>2%</span><span>伤害；同时依次召唤三针与五针，先后砸向角色，分别造成</span><span color="#ffacff">70%,80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
